reviewText:
Because I can't give it zero stars.
I'll never get my time back but I'd like my money back. Nothing inspiring and nothing learned. Belongs on free YouTube not on paid Amazon. Very disappointing
I was looking for real-life accounts from nurses regarding t heir careers and experiences. It was a good bit too general for me and I feel I wasted $10.
Used this video for a course on community health.  Stimulated a great discussion on the evolving health care system and the divide between what we want and what we can afford.
Funny and poignant nursing stories. Told by nurses and realistic. Arrived in perfect condition and on time.

Boring. I would recommend the CBS archived Nursing Diaries - much more virtual and much like shadowing nurses in the real setting. Very helpful when I presented to my nursing students. This one, forget about it.
